<p>His investigation takes him far from home, all the way to England where he uncovers a shocking secret. Ivan discovers that an army of archers is being created to combat the gangster threat in Germany. This discovery not only gives him hope but inspires him to continue his quest to end the gangster movement.</p>
<p>Meanwhile, Princess Olga travels to the capital of Germany, Berlin, where she casts her vote on the creation of the army. It is here that she meets with Alexander, her former bodyguard and Knight. He reveals to her the dire situation that Ivan has found himself in and together, they set out to rescue him.</p>
<p>Ivan's investigation leads him to Russia where he discovers a secret factory creating evil robots, a tool being used by the gangster movement to terrorize and control. This is where he encounters the Green Elephant, the former Knight who betrayed his honor for power and is now the leader of the gangster movement. Ivan is captured and his fate hangs in the balance.</p>
<p>Meanwhile, Olya and Alexander reach Russia and join the fight against the gangsters. But their rescue mission is quickly turned into a battle for survival as they too are captured. The three Knights are brought into the arena where they are to be executed in front of a cheering crowd of gangsters.</p>
<p>But just when all hope seems lost, an army of archers led by the fire manager Chebupel arrives, descending upon the arena. A fierce battle between good and evil erupts with the army of archers fighting against the army of robots.</p>
<p>In the midst of the chaos, Alexander and Ivan confront the Green Elephant, who wields a massive two-meter sword, eager to spill their blood. The battle is brutal and intense, and Alexander is wounded while Ivan falls in combat.</p>
<p>It is Mr. Xto, the coolest magician in the world, who arrives to continue the fight against the ruthless Green Elephant. However, the President manages to elude capture, slipping away in the chaos of battle.</p>
<p>Despite the loss of their comrade, the Knights emerge victorious thanks to the bravery and skill of the army of archers. With the gangster movement dealt a decisive blow, citizens begin to hope once more for a brighter future. The Knights, having proven their loyalty and bravery, become legends throughout Germany, inspiring a new generation of heroes to rise up and defend their land.</p></div>

